<title type="html"><![CDATA[4/1(Thu.)Steve chen - Co-founder of YouTube/Table topic questions(Host:William)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=485&amp;p=507#p507"><![CDATA[
4/1(Thu.)Steve chen - Co-founder of YouTube/Table topic questions(Host:William)<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000"><br />Place: 丹堤咖啡, 台北市延平南路107號2樓 (MRT 西門站4號出口)<br />Agenda:<br />07:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />07:05-7:40 pm Session 1 Group Discussion<br />07:40-8:00 pm Presentation (At least two members of each table are invited, 2 mins / each member)<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40 pm Session 2 discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Presentation~</span><br /><br /><br />Article1: Steve chen - Co-founder of YouTube<br /><br /><a href="https://youtu.be/9X9cfIwrZQo" class="postlink">https://youtu.be/9X9cfIwrZQo</a><br /><a href="https://youtu.be/ZRfj4Or2mX0" class="postlink">https://youtu.be/ZRfj4Or2mX0</a><br /><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Chen" class="postlink">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Steve_Chen</a><br /><br />1. Have you ever heard Steve Chen ? How often do you use YouTube ? Steve Chen majored in computer science and joined Papal when he was  fourth grade in the university.<br />2. Did you inspire by Steve Chen's story ? When he was 27 years old he began his startup business with his colleagues.<br />3. Is it a good idea working at a startup company and running the startup business by yourself later ?<br />4. What's your favorite video in YouTube ? Do you like to watch live streaming in YouTube ? <br />5. What are the main functions of YouTube ? Which functions do you like the most ? <br />6. Whats are the traits and qualities that every successful entrepreneur posses ? <br />7. How to structure your startup as the company grows ?<br /><br />Article2: Table topic questions<br />Questions will be prepared and asked by the host during the session.<br /><br /><span style="color: #FF0000">P.S.<br />1.因聚會地點是在咖啡店內，所以有低消80元喔。<br />2.參加三次後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />3.請帶著開放與熱情來參加自由的全英文會話聚會~</span><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=12531">Danny Lin</a> — Sat Mar 27, 2021 10:37 pm</p><hr />
]]></content>
